<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/mar/21/">&#x27a0;</a> March 21, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="experimental-gameplay-project" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://kevin-allen-jr.livejournal.com/81240.html">Experimental Gameplay Project t-shirts at Target</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Target is stocking t-shirts which come with CD-ROMs of games from the Experimental Gameplay Project. Off-the-wall short-form games *and* silk-screened T-shaped clothing? It&#8217;s like they&#8217;re IN MY MIND!</p>

