        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.popcap.com/games/mac/peggle">Peggle</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The awesome Peggle is now available for Mac, for anyone who hasn&#8217;t yet been caught in its crack-like addiction.  And only $10 to register until the end of the year.  Well worth it.</p>

