<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/sep/12/">&#x27a0;</a> September 12, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="tap-tap-revolution" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://cre.ations.net/creation/tap-tap-revolution">Tap Tap Revolution: the fast-tapping iPhone music game</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Best game so-far for the iPhone.  And once again I say: If this is the awesomeness unleashed by reverse-engineering, imagine what might be possible if Apple ever get around to releasing a proper development environment for the iPhone.</p>

